About Us
/$
$
/$
$
Peabody's is an expansive sports bar/restaurant offering billiards, games, bars and casual dining. 10,000 sq ft of clean, comfortable dining/entertainment space includes over 70 tv's, 11 professional pool tables, 8 electronic dart boards and 2 basketball machines. Since 1998, we have proudly served premium drinks and high quality food to our New Tampa/USF patrons. Expect brand name, fresh ingredients in every serving.
